## Order and Limit

### order

```ruby
# Ascending
Article.order(:created_at)
Article.order(created_at: :asc)

# Descending
Article.order(created_at: :desc)

# Multiple columns
Article.order(status: :asc, created_at: :desc)

# String (for complex ordering)
Article.order('created_at DESC, title ASC')

# Nulls first/last (PostgreSQL)
Article.order('published_at DESC NULLS LAST')
```

### limit and offset

```ruby
# Limit
Article.limit(10)

# Offset (for pagination)
Article.limit(10).offset(20)

# Better: Use pagination gem (Kaminari, Pagy)
Article.page(3).per(10)  # Kaminari
```

